\v 2 Ă‹k Obanga Apap onu Ă«ka Rwoth Yecu Kiricito Ă¶mĂŻĂŻwu gum Ă«ka kuc. 
\s1 Obanga na kweo cwinywa kĂŻbĂ«c 
