\v 3 PwĂ¶c obed both Obanga Apap ka Rwoth onu Yecu Kiricito, Apap n'obedo akĂŻca Ă«ka Obanga na kweo cwiny jĂ¶ kĂŻbĂ«c.  
\v 4 Ă‹n kweo cwinywa kĂŻ ĂŻ canwa kĂŻbĂ«c, Ă«k wan thon ekwe cwiny jĂ¶ na tye kĂŻ can na papath kĂŻ kweo cwiny na wan kikomwa enwongo kĂŻ both Obanga.  
\v 5 PĂŻ kite na can na Kiricito Ă¶dangĂ¶ opodho ĂŻ komwa na thwĂ¶nĂ«, kĂ¶manĂ¶n thon pĂŻ Kiricito wan thon ekweo cwinywa rwĂ¶k.  
\v 6 Ka wan Ă«dangĂ¶ can, manĂ¶n mĂŻĂ¶ ekweo cwinywu Ă«ka inwongo unu larĂ«. Ka ekweo cwinywa, manĂ¶n thon mĂŻĂ¶ ekweo cwinywu, mĂŻĂ¶ un ĂŻcakĂ¶ nwongo tĂ«kĂ¶ mĂ« dangĂ¶ kit can na wan thon Ă«dangĂ¶.  
